creator: Incentivio Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Order Bread Zeppelin for pickup, delivery, and earn points towards rewards.

About Bread Zeppelin
We offer an array of fresh ingredients served in a bowl or signature “Zeppelin”, a cored-out, fresh-baked artisan baguette. This unique twist creates a tasty alternative to the often messy wrap that easily falls apart. Bread Zeppelin is a convenient option that satisfies and nourishes without the guilt by preparing high quality meals with fresh and natural ingredients. We offer many signature salads as options for guests, or you can choose to build your own, all of which include house-made dressings, fresh grilled proteins, and served by our engaging employees.

Mobile Ordering
Place your order through your phone by selecting your restaurant location, pickup or delivery, and the time you’d like to get your order.

Eat Bread, Earn Bread
- You’ll earn points for ordering online or scanning when you pay at a restaurant
- Use the app to scan for points and use your rewards at a restaurant or apply them to an online order
- Points and rewards can take up to 48 hours to show in your account
- Earn 10 points for every $1 spent
